            <score-icon-critics size="1.5" sentiment="POSITIVE"></score-icon-critics>
            <span></span>
          </div>
          
            <span slot="review">[La Dolce Vita] propelled Fellini into the front rank of international directors.</span>
            <rt-link slot="review-link" context="link" href="https://www.theaustralian.com.au/arts/review/finding-fellinis-finest-david-stratton-remembers-i-vitelloni-and-la-dolce-vita/news-story/25f6cab215aec0d1c317c3d17ea2389a" target="_blank">
              Go to Full Review
            </rt-link>
          
          <rt-button
            slot="options-menu"
            theme="transparent"
            data-MediaCriticsReviewsManager="optionsMenuBtn:click"
            data-encrypted-publication-id="xlbWOgyE"
