            <score-icon-critics size="1.5" sentiment="POSITIVE"></score-icon-critics>
            <span></span>
          </div>
          
            <span slot="review">Fellini is noted for his mastery of contrasts, his uncanny ability to find off-beat and bizarre occurrences which expose both the little and gross facets of life... Its impact is violent. Its irony is grim. Its wit is sardonic. Its pathos is awesome.</span>
            <rt-link slot="review-link" context="link" href="https://archive.org/details/sim_jet_1961-06-22_20_9/page/65/mode/1up?view=theater" target="_blank">
